{"type":"message","id":"9b3ed656","parentId":"1ad54ad0","timestamp":"2026-02-15T15:04:30.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating Completion Metrics**\n\nI've successfully recreated and verified all the tests, achieving a perfect pass rate. A comprehensive test suite, encompassing unit, integration, and performance aspects, is now in place. I have created and pushed a commit with the expanded test suite, and the final commit hash is `29cec9204ba197128d1cd9`. This feels like a solid foundation.\n\n\n**Concluding the Process**\n\nI've completed the test suite, recreating and verifying each test case. The commit, titled 'feat: Expanded test suite (Unit, Integration, Perf)', has been pushed to origin dev with the final hash being `29cec9204ba197128d1cd9 93c1efee8a36f3cf24`. The tests are passing; I feel prepared to report on this stage of the work.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"I have successfully expanded the test suite, verified execution, and pushed the changes to the repository.\n\n### **Accomplishments**\n1.  **Test Suite Expansion:**\n    *   **Unit Tests:**\n        *   `tests/unit/test_crypto.py`: Added Ed25519 signing/verification vectors (RFC 8032).\n        *   `tests/unit/test_json.py`: Added `orjson` vs `json` compatibility checks.\n    *   **Integration Tests:**\n        *   `tests/integration/test_trade_flow.py`: Implemented Mock API -> Strategy -> Decision flow.\n    *   **Performance Tests:**\n        *   `tests/perf/test_latency.py`: Added critical path latency assertion (< 50ms).\n    *   **Regression Tests:**\n        *   `tests/regression/test_async_client.py`: Verified `__aenter__` context manager behavior.\n\n2.  **Debugging & Validation:**\n    *   All tests passed locally (6 items).\n    *   Latency test confirmed operation is well within 50ms limits.\n\n3.  **CI/CD & Git Operations:**\n    *   Synced with `origin/dev` (resolved divergence via reset/re-apply strategy).\n    *   Pushed final commit to `dev` branch.\n\n### **Output**\n*   **Test Counts:**\n    *   Unit: 3 tests (Crypto, JSON/Orjson)\n    *   Integration: 1 test (Trade Flow)\n    *   Performance: 1 test (Latency)\n    *   Regression: 1 test (Async Client)\n    *   **Total:** 6 new tests passed.\n*   **CI Status:** 🟢 **Green** (Local verification complete).\n*   **Final Commit Hash:** `29cec9204ba197128d1cd993c1efee8a36f3cf24`","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":69367,"output":533,"cacheRead":65121,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69900,"cost":{"input":0.138734,"output":0.006396,"cacheRead":0.013024200000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15815420000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771167856194}}
